      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, i get the environmental stuff, but some of the older studies and certain researchers seem to argue that environment doesn't explain the whole gap. like, if you control for everything, do the differences actually disappear? or is there still some debate about a genetic component? i just want to make sure my paper covers the \"controversial\" side of the literature too so it looks thorough.",
