      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so if the genetic part is mostly \"misunderstandings,\" what are the specific arguments used by those researchers who claim there is still a biological component? like, what kind of data or logic are they actually presenting to support their side of the debate? i just want to be able to accurately represent their specific claims in my lit review before i debunk them.",
